Pará (
<figureCitation id="13622A28FFBEFF842C60625AFF4BFC2E" captionStart="FIGURES 57 – 59" captionStartId="17.[151,264,1763,1785]" captionTargetBox="[158,1433,589,1732]" captionTargetId="figure@17.[151,1436,589,1742]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="FIGURES 57 – 59. Geographical distribution of Xenopygus species. 57, X. analis; 58, X. bicolor (dots) + X. confusus (triangles); 59, X. cordovensis (dots) + X. sancticamillus, sp. nov. (triangles) + X. petilicolis, sp. nov. (squares)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/265275/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="74">
Fig. 
<number id="3D91248AFFBEFF8429996279FF4BFC2E" box="[151,183,871,896]" pageId="15" pageNumber="74" value="58.0">58</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
